<div id="review_2889676648" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2889676648" />
    <a title="Katy Elmore" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/78221800-katy-elmore"><img alt="Katy Elmore" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1530563690p2/78221800.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2889676648?book_show_action=true">Jul 16, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Katy Elmore" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Katy Elmore" href="/user/show/78221800-katy-elmore">Katy Elmore</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2889676648" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer549648466792812942">Hm...I don&apos;t really know what to think of this book. I really enjoyed Cameron&apos;s narrative and I think he had some really good insights on what it&apos;s like to be mentally distraught/ill and in therapy. Otherwise, though, I think this guy was trying way too hard to make this novel Catcher in the Rye. So just read Catcher in the Rye. It&apos;s better.</span>
  <span id="freeText549648466792812942" style="display:none">Hm...I don't really know what to think of this book. I really enjoyed Cameron's narrative and I think he had some really good insights on what it's like to be mentally distraught/ill and in therapy. Otherwise, though, I think this guy was trying way too hard to make this novel Catcher in the Rye. So just read Catcher in the Rye. It's better.</span>
  <a data-text-id="549648466792812942" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


