<div id="review_981776601" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/981776601" />
    <a title="Claudia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4910002-claudia"><img alt="Claudia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1345209109p2/4910002.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/981776601?book_show_action=true">Jun 29, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Claudia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Claudia" href="/user/show/4910002-claudia">Claudia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer981776601" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9539942108715306439">Great book. I have underlined quite a few passages. Sarcasm and deep sentimentality were woven together on so many pages. A very human book, talking about both first world and deeply disturbing problems. I had respect for the fact that Cameron wasn&apos;t afraid to show both young, older and elderly adults getting caught up in behaving like jerks at times. And the story made me care. It moved me. Will investigate more by this author.</span>
  <span id="freeText9539942108715306439" style="display:none">Great book. I have underlined quite a few passages. Sarcasm and deep sentimentality were woven together on so many pages. A very human book, talking about both first world and deeply disturbing problems. I had respect for the fact that Cameron wasn't afraid to show both young, older and elderly adults getting caught up in behaving like jerks at times. And the story made me care. It moved me. Will investigate more by this author.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9539942108715306439" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
